The paper deals with the efficient management of large sequences of multidimensional data, which is a common problem in database systems (cs.DB) and data structures (cs.DS). The paper also discusses aggregation queries, which are a common topic in information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper proposes a flexible representation that can be tailored to specific queries, which is a common theme in artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
